---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
     Adept in marketing/customer analytics and statistical modelling. Actively enhancing 
     skills in advanced Machine Learning techniques. Proven expertise in leveraging data to drive strategic decision-making 
     and efficiency.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Head of Impact & Market Intelligence"
      subtitle="From 12/2021 to 05/2023 at Proximity Designs (Remote)"
    >
    Delivered monthly data-driven market and consumer insights, enabling the marketing team to identify target audiences and measure the effectiveness of marketing efforts. Supervised 25 projects focused on digital marketing performance analytics, post-ad survey analysis, A/B testing and causal analysis for product impact measurement, cohort analysis, collectively contributing to a 30% increase in user adoption rate. Achieved a 70% improvement in project delivery time by streamlining and optimising data collection processes.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Founder"
      subtitle="From 11/2020 to 05/2022 at Insights Plus"
    >
      Provided research and advanced analytics services, by leveraging market assessment, statistical modelling, and demand forecasting, to technology start-ups and organisations, contributing to new product launches and improved market positioning.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Senior Associate, Insights & Analytics"
      subtitle="From 09/2017 to 10/2020  at Yoma Strategic Holdings"
    >
      Applied various analytics techniques focused on marketing analytics (brand equity measurement, marketing mix modelling), and customer analytics (retention, customer behaviour, segmentation) to support marketing decision-making processes for 10+ business units.Led full-cycle research and analytics projects, from data collection to presentation of findings to C-suite stakeholders, contributing to key decisions on a $25 M investment project.Collaborated with leading consultancy firms such as Kantar, Nielsen, Thura Swiss for outsourced projects.

    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Business Analyst, Business Development"
      subtitle="From 11/2015 to 08/2017 at Yoma Strategic Holdings"
    >
      Developed financial models (ROI analysis and valuation) and conducted in-depth market research to facilitate partnerships with globally recognised brands such as METRO AG.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Master of Science, Business Analytics"
      subtitle="2024 - University of Essex (Pass with distinction)"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bacher of Science, Business Management"
      subtitle="2014 - National Management Degree College"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a href="https://certificates.mavenanalytics.io/66096232-6b42-48ce-950e-686aa28e4be8#gs.6pvyd8" target="_blank"> Data Science in Python: Classification </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://certificates.mavenanalytics.io/becec0ac-939d-4548-9252-6adf9fcd3eea#gs.6pw9y8" target="_blank"> Advanced MySQL Data Analysis </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://basno.com/pubhxwp3" target="_blank"> CFA Level 1 Badge </a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Tools & Technologies</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>MySQL</li>
    <li>R</li>
    <li>SPSS</li>
    <li>Tableau</li>
    <li>PowerBI</li>
    <li>Google Analytics</li>
    <li>VS Code
    <li>Docker</li>
